{
  "stem": "24346.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father was left there with other relatives.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were separated, couldn't get there no more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's how my father wound up in Krasnik, and my mother and my brother, [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Leib, ?] and I were left in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was there in Krasnik with his in-laws, because he married a cousin of mine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's like, you've got the name on the list I gave you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My uncle, they had seven beautiful daughters and one son.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, a lot of Jewish people, intermarried between cousins and cousins.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he married, and they went there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They rented a whole house, because one that we had as inheritance wasn't enough for everybody, because you've got quite a list of people we had.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he rented-- it was a well-off uncle, also-- Uncle Falek.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he rented a house, and all the in-laws with the married daughters-- in fact, all were married, because the last one, Gucia, got married during the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then it was already a civil ceremony-- quiet, nothing elaborate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because when I remember, when my brother got married, it was in a real hall, compared to the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a beautiful wedding, pictures and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the last, that was the youngest daughter, she got married, too, because they didn't want a boy and girl get together, so they married them off at the civil ceremony-- a rabbi, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he was middle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Middle, that's correct.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You've got it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The brother in the small town, we only got one letter from there to-- we are well, we are doing good-- and no more.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't know anything from them till after the war, when I met people from that city, and I asked them.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
